  "text": "Detection of the underlying genetic population among the studied cowpea accessions was carried out with the Structure software [CITATION_1] . Three populations (K = 3) were assumed and indicated with blue, green and red colours. Different numbers were tried for K and finally 3 accepted with admixture ancestry model. Length of burnin was 5000 and the number of MCMC was set at 10000.",
